Text: May I ask you why you bother to upload this already existing torrent? The only thing you are doing is splitting the swarm..
just may i ask what the your problem with that as this is being done on all the torrent ??

No. It is not being done on all the torrents. The problem is that when the first torrent is trying to build up a healthy seeder/leecher ratio, you upload another one, and the process must start over from the beginning.

More duplicate torrents = shittier seeder/leecher ratios.
